|ID|OPERATOR                            |NAME    |
--------------------------------------------------
|0 |PX COORDINATOR MERGE SORT           |        |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR                |:EX10001|
|2 |  └─MATERIAL                        |        |
|3 |    └─MERGE DISTINCT                |        |
|4 |      └─EXCHANGE IN MERGE SORT DISTR|        |
|5 |        └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH) |:EX10000|
|6 |          └─MERGE DISTINCT          |        |
|7 |            └─SORT                  |        |
|8 |              └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR   |        |
|9 |                └─TABLE GET         |lyq_test|
==================================================
